## ⚙️ Membre 3 : Abdellah — Infrastructure & Services Transversaux

### 📁 Dossiers de travail
```
discovery-service/
config-service/
gateway-service/
docker-compose.yml
pom.xml (parent)
setup-config-repo.bat
```

### 📝 Tâches détaillées

| # | Tâche | Fichiers concernés |
|---|-------|--------------------|
| **Discovery Service (Eureka)** | | |
| 1 | **Créer le Discovery Service** : serveur Eureka pour l'enregistrement et la découverte des services | `discovery-service/src/.../DiscoveryServiceApplication.java` |
| 2 | **Configuration Eureka** : application.yml (port 8761, dashboard) | [discovery-service/src/main/resources/application.yml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/discovery-service/src/main/resources/application.yml) |
| 3 | **POM Discovery** : dépendances (spring-cloud-starter-netflix-eureka-server) | [discovery-service/pom.xml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/discovery-service/pom.xml) |
| 4 | **Dockerfile Discovery** | [discovery-service/Dockerfile](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/discovery-service/Dockerfile) |
| **Config Service** | | |
| 5 | **Créer le Config Service** : serveur de configuration centralisée (Git-backed) | `config-service/src/.../ConfigServiceApplication.java` |
| 6 | **Configuration Config Server** : application.yml (port 8888, lien vers Git repo) | [config-service/src/main/resources/application.yml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/config-service/src/main/resources/application.yml) |
| 7 | **POM Config** : dépendances (spring-cloud-config-server) | [config-service/pom.xml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/config-service/pom.xml) |
| 8 | **Dockerfile Config** | [config-service/Dockerfile](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/config-service/Dockerfile) |
| 9 | **Script setup config repo** : setup-config-repo.bat pour initialiser le repo Git local | [setup-config-repo.bat](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/setup-config-repo.bat) |
| **Gateway Service** | | |
| 10 | **Créer le Gateway Service** : API Gateway (Spring Cloud Gateway) | `gateway-service/src/.../GatewayServiceApplication.java` |
| 11 | **Configuration Gateway** : routes vers video-service et user-service | [gateway-service/src/main/resources/application.yml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/gateway-service/src/main/resources/application.yml) |
| 12 | **POM Gateway** : dépendances (spring-cloud-starter-gateway) | [gateway-service/pom.xml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/gateway-service/pom.xml) |
| 13 | **Dockerfile Gateway** | [gateway-service/Dockerfile](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/gateway-service/Dockerfile) |
| **Docker & Parent POM** | | |
| 14 | **Docker Compose** : orchestration de tous les services (2 MySQL, 5 services Spring) | [docker-compose.yml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/docker-compose.yml) |
| 15 | **POM Parent** : définir les modules, versions Spring Boot et Spring Cloud | [pom.xml](file:///c:/Users/whhaj/IdeaProjects/StreamForge-ModernMicroservicesStreaming/pom.xml) (racine) |

### 📊 Volume estimé
- **3 classes Java** (une par service) + 3 application.yml + 3 Dockerfiles + 3 POM
- **docker-compose.yml** complet avec healthchecks et networks
- **Complexité** : ⭐⭐⭐ (configuration Spring Cloud, pas de logique métier complexe)

### 🔗 Dépendance
- **Aucune dépendance** sur le code métier → peut travailler de façon indépendante
- Doit juste connaître les **noms des services** (VIDEO-SERVICE, USER-SERVICE) et les **ports** (8081, 8082) pour le routing

